definition: Qianjiang sub-prefecture level city in Hubei

sentences.english: Qianjiang City endeavored to improve the employment environment for rural workers in cities.
sentences.chinese: 潛江市着力改善農民進城就業環境。

sentences.english: The roadbed of a 300-metre section rail in Qianjiang city collapsed on Friday.
sentences.chinese: 星期五，潛江市300米長的鐵路路基塌陷。
